// @test regression/INV041-while-condition-bool
// @description Non-bool while conditions are TV's CE10101 with blockName "while", anchored at the condition expression (probed `while close` 4:7 and `while n` int). Bool conditions stay clean. See INV041.
// @expects parse: success
// @expects errors: 2
// @expects error: line=4, column=7, message=/The condition of the .while. statement must evaluate to a .bool. value/
// @expects error: line=8, column=7, message=/The condition of the .while. statement must evaluate to a .bool. value/

//@version=6
indicator("INV041 while")
i = 0
while close
    i := i + 1
    break
n = 3
while n
    i := i + 1
    break
while i < 10
    i := i + 1
plot(i)
